Privacy Policy for News Pilot AI

Introduction

Welcome to News Pilot AI! We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our service, which is built on OpenAI's platform.

Information We Collect

1. User-Provided Information
When you use News Pilot AI, you may provide us with the following information:

Content for Analysis: The text of articles, blog posts, or academic papers you submit for analysis.
Contact Information: If you contact us for support, we may collect your name and email address.
2. Automatically Collected Information
We may also collect certain information automatically, including:

Usage Data: Information about how you interact with our service, such as the pages viewed and the actions taken.
Device Information: Information about the device you use to access our service, including IP address, browser type, and operating system.
How We Use Your Information

We use the information we collect for the following purposes:

To Provide and Improve Our Service: Analyzing your submitted content to provide feedback and improve our analysis algorithms.
To Communicate with You: Responding to your inquiries and providing customer support.
To Ensure Security: Protecting our service and users from fraudulent or malicious activity.
Data Sharing and Disclosure

We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties except in the following circumstances:

Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information if required to do so by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities.
Service Providers: We may share information with third-party service providers who assist us in operating our service.
Integration with OpenAI

Our service utilizes OpenAI's platform to process and analyze content. By using News Pilot AI, you acknowledge that your submitted content will be processed by OpenAI. OpenAI's use of data is governed by their Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.

Data Retention

We retain your personal information only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this privacy policy. Content submitted for analysis is processed by OpenAI and is deleted after processing. We do not store any analyzed content.

Security

We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

Your Rights

You have the following rights regarding your personal information:

Access and Correction: You can request access to your personal information and ask us to correct any inaccuracies.
Deletion: You can request the deletion of your personal information.
Objection: You can object to the processing of your personal information in certain circumstances.
To exercise these rights, please contact us at [your contact email].

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new privacy policy on this page. Changes are effective as of the "Last Updated" date at the top of this page.
